{"tid":2341642,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)聖誕特別節目2","createTime":"2020-12-26T14:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T20:34:46.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"39b9011207977f7d96c600369068f20de2633265","tid":2341642,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=dbdc0804\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=4de3459d\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=20d85e00\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/cf/Krampus_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fcf%2FKrampus_Poster.jpg&h=c4abe94e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f9/Parenttrapposter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff9%2FParenttrapposter.jpg&h=d717825e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/images/video_poster/2018/2018101214211820984aea26ce859b99d6ddec737f8ce8d92f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dramaqueen.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fvideo_poster%2F2018%2F2018101214211820984aea26ce859b99d6ddec737f8ce8d92f.jpg&h=ac9fbd17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事敘述一個不為人熟知的暗黑版聖誕節傳說,徹底顛覆我們對歡樂假期的想像。從小在衝突不斷的家庭中長大，年輕的麥斯對聖誕節早已不抱任何期望。但他一點也不知道，這種缺乏歡樂節日的精神已經燃起坎卜斯的憤怒，喚醒這一位古老的邪惡妖怪來懲罰不相信聖誕節的人們。當家喻戶曉的節慶主角化身成為惡魔開始攻擊這個破碎的家庭，迫使他們挺身為家人戰鬥，如果他們希望活下去...<br />\n<br />\n2.荷莉&middot;帕克是一位11歲的小女孩，與父親在加州納帕縣的快樂的生活著，而父親尼克&middot;帕克是一位成功的葡萄園主人。荷莉的雙胞胎姊妹安妮&middot;詹姆士和母親住在倫敦，母親伊莉莎白&middot;詹姆士為一位婚紗設計師。這對姊妹完全不知道彼此的存在。<br />\n某年暑假，荷莉和安妮碰巧都參加了同一個夏令營。一開始，兩人視彼此為敵人，但兩人都有一些共同的特質：對草莓過敏，撲克牌高手，擅長惡作劇。某次他們在對對方惡作劇之後，輔導員將他們隔離且要求他們住在同一間寢室，他們便很快發現彼此的身世秘密。之後，他們計畫在夏令營結束時交換彼此的身份，去見他們無法相見的父母親..<br />\n<br />\n3.聖誕節當天，小女孩凱特在回味過往家人拍攝的影片時，意外發現疑似聖誕老人現身的蛛絲馬跡，遂與兄長泰迪合作守夜，打算用攝影機捕捉聖誕老人蒞臨的畫面。當晚兩人的守候也沒有落空，凱特與泰迪甚至還進一步偷溜上了聖誕老人的雪橇，卻因此使聖誕老人受到驚嚇，導致雪橇出了事故，使無數的孩子即將面臨收不到禮物的危機。闖禍的兄妹倆便與聖誕老人合作，攜手挽救聖誕節<br />\n<br />\n4.因為不滿媽媽的新戀情，步入青春期的少女凱特離家出走，隨後落腳北極，那裡卻有個調皮精靈正密謀要破壞聖誕節。<br />\n<br />\n10 10PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能會播返NEO同JL<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=3e0d4508\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=88343fb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f40275fcd816229d4830909d607d252fd4a893","tid":2341642,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c4f1ec850c3dd0d39cad4bd70d3bc5d6e7a9f4","tid":2341642,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7d3e6f944ab211ccb6944bfd0cf833625bbdda","tid":2341642,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87c1f0b8385ec0d2376c2d708a952b24358ce32","tid":2341642,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T17:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6681fa208a97068097de65b7c2af5870800707ce","tid":2341642,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T19:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd31b3d31410c10edd53f7687b914b28022d279","tid":2341642,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T20:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\